channel.description:

item.title: I don't want to leech,
item.dc:creator: @Cheesehunk Cheesehunk
item.description:
@Cheesehunk wrote:

[quote=“RdSoxFan618, post:1, topic:5676”]but is it ok if you look on other ppl’s scripts to find out how to do stuff, like RadialRoadWalk?

If I needed somethng to help me am I allowed to look on their and write my own?[/quote]

Thats how I learned.

I was never much of a person to ask questions, I would just look at others code until I mastered what I wanted to. I would never know Arrays, RadialRoadWalk, and a lot of other stuff if it wasn’t for looking through others code to see how it worked.
